{"tid":2343021,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「安心出行」成表忠道具｜ 搞港姐公投大敗黑歷史 開發商埋堆中資恐私隱「送中」","createTime":"2020-12-27T14:49:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T15:29:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"465b511caaacf187ae188a987b4320e87b7c36f8","tid":2343021,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T14:49:18.000Z","msg":"「安心出行」成表忠道具｜<br />\n搞港姐公投大敗黑歷史 開發商埋堆中資恐私隱「送中」<br />\n#壹仔專題－壹週刊 Next <br />\n原刊日期：20201210<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nodT1uBnAF4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnodT1uBnAF4&d=%2BrTTj2V4oNsvrkryR3gjd7HKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=59e50d48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nodT1uBnAF4</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n壹週刊 NEXT<br />\n676K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎肆虐近一年，港府雖延遲推港版健康碼，但卻「改頭換面」，改推應用程式「安心出行」，配合處所張貼的二維碼（QR Code），志在要市民自願記錄行蹤，方便政府追蹤及預防病源，結果爆發私隱安全疑雲，市民擔心一但使用應用程式，政府或從程式中伺機讀取手機資料。不過建制派議員紛紛護航，只要「唔scan唔畀入」，就能「焗」市民用「安心出行」。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"https://s.nextmag.hk/e/uvoZHOoP5bb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmag.hk%2Fe%2FuvoZHOoP5bb&d=%2BrTTj2V4oNsvrkryR3gjd7HKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=65dda3b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmag.hk/e/uvoZHOoP5bb</a><br />\n-----------------------------"},{"pid":"88c9907adac9a2f7eb61a51df89cb3019e743192","tid":2343021,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T14:53:17.000Z","msg":"港共全部都係垃圾"},{"pid":"9f453ada20e98391fe7b7ab1c0df60d1d2596111","tid":2343021,"uid":39710,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T15:29:23.000Z","msg":"都唔撚見有人係街用個APP"}]}